\gcd(m,n)=1
(\Bbb{Z}/m\Bbb{Z})\otimes_{\Bbb{Z}}(\Bbb{Z}/n\Bbb{Z})\cong\Bbb{Z}/\gcd(m,n)\Bbb{Z},
(\Bbb{Z}/m\Bbb{Z})\times\Bbb{Z}/n\Bbb{Z})\ \longrightarrow\ \Bbb{Z}/gcd(m,n)\Bbb{Z}:\ (a,b)\ \longmapsto\ a\cdot b.
